Generic single-database configuration with Alembic.

## Installation

Install alembic:
```bash
pip install alembic
```

## Usage

### Create a new migration (auto-generate from models)

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Add new column to users"
```

### Apply migrations (upgrade to head)

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback to previous version

```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### Show current revision

```bash
alembic current
```

### Show migration history

```bash
alembic history
```

## Initial Setup

The initial migration should capture the current state of the database schema.

```bash
# Generate initial migration
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Initial schema"

# Apply it
alembic upgrade head
```
